BUSINESS RULE SPECIFICATIONS

RULE INFORMATION

Statement:  _A student's test can only be scheduled to take place during the proctoring center's hour of operation. The test must be started and finished during proctoring center's hours.

Constraint: _Check to see if the time interval selected exists within the time scheduled for the proctoring center to be open.

